description: Coming off of his third win on NK, Sebastian Keys is undefeated and confident. He has 3 black belts in martial arts and plans to rely on his training to take him to his fourth win. He knows his opponent is a veteran on NK and has seen some of his previous matches. Sebastian is going to use DJ's body momentum against him, in order to slam him to the mat, hard! DJ is not intimidated by Sebastian's black belts. He feels his experience on NK is all he will need to gain the points required to take home another win and feed his big, uncut, cock to Sebastian. They both are ready to fight and make the loser his bitch for the day.
title: DJ vs Sebastian Keys
